headline: America's Top Eco-Friendly Cities for Car-Free Transit
summary: How we navigate our cities plays a big role in sustainability — but not every place makes it easy to go car-free. Today, Realtor.com® and location intelligence company Local Logic unveiled a new ranking of America's Top Eco-Friendly Cities for Car-Free Transit, highlighting the places where walking, biking, and public transit are not only viable, but widely used.
